data.description: Welcome to your little slice of heaven just outside of town! This open floor plan home features a spacious living room, dining room and kitchen. Great for entertaining family and friends! The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet and bedrooms 2 and 3 are located upstairs with a full bath. The half bath is located adjacent to the laundry room.  There is a detached garage ideal for storage or a work shop. Plenty of parking space. You can watch your kids play while sitting back on your front porch. Do not wait!! Make an appointment today!!
